      "amount": "1 teaspoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "turmeric powder",
      "amount": "1/2 teaspoon"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat the ghee in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the cumin seeds and let them sizzle for a few seconds.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the grated ginger and minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the chicken pieces and cook until they are browned and cooked through.",
    "Add the soy sauce, coriander powder, and turmeric powder, and stir well.",
    "Add the basmati rice and stir well to combine with the chicken and spice mixture.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 10 minutes or until the rice is cooked and the liquid is absorbed."
  ],
